<p class="ql-align-center">电器修理、义诊、理发等志愿服务活动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201205/dfbfca0dc0e54caa89019ccbcfd5c373.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
